# huuman Design System

Mobile-first, dark-only health app. Every UI change must use these tokens, components, and patterns.

## Design Tokens (globals.css)

### Surfaces (elevation = lighter, not shadows)
- `bg-surface-base` (#09090b) -- page background
- `bg-surface-raised` (#18181b) -- cards, inputs, list items
- `bg-surface-overlay` (#27272a) -- sheets, drawers, popovers
- `bg-surface-elevated` (#3f3f46) -- hover/active states, tooltips

### Borders
- `border-border-subtle` -- faint separators
- `border-border-default` -- standard borders (cards, inputs)
- `border-border-strong` -- emphasized borders

### Text hierarchy
- `text-text-primary` (#fafafa) -- headings, important text
- `text-text-secondary` (#a1a1aa) -- body text, descriptions
- `text-text-tertiary` (#71717a) -- labels, captions
- `text-text-muted` (#52525b) -- timestamps, disabled, placeholders

### Domain accent colors (3 intensities each)
Each domain has `-muted` (backgrounds), default (text/icons), `-bright` (interactive):
- Cardio: `text-domain-cardio`, `bg-domain-cardio-muted`, `text-domain-cardio-bright`
- Strength: `text-domain-strength`, `bg-domain-strength-muted`, `text-domain-strength-bright`
- Mindfulness: `text-domain-mindfulness`, `bg-domain-mindfulness-muted`, `text-domain-mindfulness-bright`
- Nutrition: `text-domain-nutrition`, `bg-domain-nutrition-muted`, `text-domain-nutrition-bright`
- Sleep: `text-domain-sleep`, `bg-domain-sleep-muted`, `text-domain-sleep-bright`

### Semantic colors
- `text-semantic-success` / `bg-semantic-success` -- completions, positive
- `text-semantic-warning` / `bg-semantic-warning` -- caution, attention
- `text-semantic-error` / `bg-semantic-error` -- errors, destructive

### Radii
- `rounded-radius-sm` (8px), `rounded-radius-md` (12px), `rounded-radius-lg` (16px), `rounded-radius-xl` (20px)

## Typography
Font: Inter (loaded via `next/font/google` in layout.tsx).

| Class | Size | Use |
|---|---|---|
| `text-xs` | 11px | timestamps, metadata, badges |
| `text-sm` | 13px | labels, captions, secondary |
| `text-base` | 15px | body, chat messages |
| `text-lg` | 17px | card titles, section headers |
| `text-xl` | 20px | page titles |
| `text-2xl` | 24px | hero numbers |

Weights: `font-normal` (400), `font-medium` (500), `font-semibold` (600).

## Motion (lib/motion.ts)

Import from `@/lib/motion`. Never define inline spring/transition values.

### Springs
- `spring.snappy` -- button presses, toggles, quick feedback
- `spring.smooth` -- drawers, sheets, page transitions
- `spring.bouncy` -- achievements, completion celebrations

### Press feedback (whileTap)
- `press.button` (scale: 0.97) -- all tappable buttons
- `press.card` (scale: 0.99) -- tappable cards
- `press.compact` (scale: 0.95) -- inline/contextual buttons (between button and icon)
- `press.icon` (scale: 0.92) -- icon-only buttons

### Transitions
- `transition.fade` -- opacity changes (150ms)
- `transition.slide` -- position changes (smooth spring)
- `transition.expand` -- height/width changes (250ms)

**Rule: every tappable element MUST have `whileTap` from press presets.**

## Haptics (lib/haptics.ts)

Import from `@/lib/haptics`. Call on meaningful interactions.

- `haptics.light()` -- tab switches, toggles, selections
- `haptics.medium()` -- button taps, sheet open/close
- `haptics.heavy()` -- destructive actions
- `haptics.success()` -- session completed, plan generated

**iOS Safari caveat:** `navigator.vibrate()` is not supported on iOS Safari. All haptics calls are silent there. To compensate, `Button` and `IconButton` include `active:brightness-110/125` CSS for visual press feedback that works on all platforms without JS.

## Components (components/ui/)

Always use these instead of raw HTML elements:

| Component | Import | Use instead of |
|---|---|---|
| `<Button>` | `@/components/ui/Button` | `<button>` with hand-rolled classes |
| `<IconButton>` | `@/components/ui/IconButton` | icon-only `<button>` elements |
| `<Input>` | `@/components/ui/Input` | `<input>` or `<textarea>` |
| `<Toggle>` | `@/components/ui/Toggle` | custom checkbox/toggle switches |
| `<Badge>` | `@/components/ui/Badge` | status spans with domain colors |
| `<Skeleton>` | `@/components/ui/Skeleton` | loading placeholders |
| `<Card>` | `@/components/ui/Card` | `Card`, `Card.Header`, `Card.Body`, `Card.Footer` |
| `<Sheet>` | `@/components/ui/Sheet` | the old Drawer component (now Vaul-based) |
| `<TabBar>` | `@/components/ui/TabBar` | bottom navigation |

Toast: call `toast()` / `toast.success()` / `toast.error()` from `sonner`. Toaster is mounted in root layout.

## Touch targets

All standalone tappable elements must be at least **44px** in both dimensions (Apple HIG minimum). When the visual element must be smaller, use `min-h-[44px] min-w-[44px]` to keep the hit area accessible.

- `IconButton` sm = 36px visual + 44px hit area, md = 44px, lg = 48px
- `Button` sm/md enforce `min-h-[44px]`
- Never create a raw `<button>` with `h-7` / `h-8` -- use `IconButton` or `Button`

## Anti-patterns (NEVER do these)

1. **Never use raw zinc values** -- use semantic tokens (`bg-surface-raised` not `bg-zinc-900/50`)
2. **Never define inline springs** -- import from `@/lib/motion`
3. **Never create a `<button>` without whileTap** -- use `<Button>` or `<IconButton>`
4. **Never use `hover:` without `active:`** -- mobile has no hover. Prefer `whileTap`.
5. **Never use spinners for loading** -- use `<Skeleton>` components
6. **Never hardcode spacing** -- use the 4px grid via Tailwind spacing utilities
7. **Never forget safe-area padding** -- bottom bars need `pb-[env(safe-area-inset-bottom)]`
8. **Never create touch targets below 44px** -- use `IconButton`/`Button` which enforce minimums

## Domain color mapping

When rendering domain-specific UI (sessions, cards, badges):
```
const domainColors = {
  cardio: { text: 'text-domain-cardio', bg: 'bg-domain-cardio-muted', bright: 'text-domain-cardio-bright', glow: 'shadow-glow-cardio' },
  strength: { text: 'text-domain-strength', bg: 'bg-domain-strength-muted', bright: 'text-domain-strength-bright', glow: 'shadow-glow-strength' },
  mindfulness: { text: 'text-domain-mindfulness', bg: 'bg-domain-mindfulness-muted', bright: 'text-domain-mindfulness-bright', glow: 'shadow-glow-mindfulness' },
  nutrition: { text: 'text-domain-nutrition', bg: 'bg-domain-nutrition-muted', bright: 'text-domain-nutrition-bright', glow: 'shadow-glow-nutrition' },
  sleep: { text: 'text-domain-sleep', bg: 'bg-domain-sleep-muted', bright: 'text-domain-sleep-bright', glow: 'shadow-glow-sleep' },
};
```
